},
"101": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "101",
&"next_id": "102",
&"text": "Apart from my bed still being annoying, my room is pretty cozy now",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"102": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "102",
&"next_id": "103",
&"text": "It feels like my secret agent hideout 😎",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"103": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "103",
&"next_id": "104",
&"text": "Oh by the way",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"104": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "104",
&"next_id": "105",
&"text": "Nina texted me this morning",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"105": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "105",
&"next_id": "106",
&"text": "She said she had a great time at the club",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"106": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "106",
&"next_id": "107",
&"text": "And that I should give it a chance",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"107": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "107",
&"next_id": "108",
&"text": "She's asked me if I wanted to go next weekend  💀",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"108": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "108",
&"next_id": "109",
&"text": "Thought: I don't know if I want to...",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"109": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "109",
&"next_id": "110",
&"text": "What did you say?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"11": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "11",
&"next_id": "12",
&"text": "Yeah 🥰",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"110": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "110",
&"next_id": "111",
&"text": "I haven't replied yet",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"111": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "111",
&"next_id": "112",
&"text": "I do want to hang out again",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"112": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "112",
&"next_id": "113",
&"text": "But I don't know if I want to try again 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"113": {
&"character": "Player",
&"id": "113",
&"next_id": "114",
&"text": "You can just tell her you'll consider it",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"114": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "114",
&"next_id": "115",
&"text": "Omg true",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"115": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "115",
&"next_id": "116",
&"text": "I'll see how the week goes and wait to see if you also have any free time hehe",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"116": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "116",
&"next_id": "117",
&"text": "Thanks for talking this through with me 🥹",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"117": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "117",
&"next_id": "118",
