raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Morning! 😊
Player: Morning!
Player: How'd the call with your mom go?
Mabel: It was really nice!
Mabel: I told her all about yesterday LOL
Mabel: Thought: Well.. Maybe not EVERYTHING
Mabel: The dorm, classes starting tomorrow, if I made friends
Mabel: The usual mom stuff haha
Player: That's sweet
Mabel: Yeah 🥰
Mabel: She also asked about you!
Player: Oh yeah? What did you say?
Mabel: She wanted to know if you were taking care of me 😌
Player: I hope you said yes 😂
Mabel: It's a secret!
Mabel: Thought: I told her you were the best
Mabel: I also told her about my closet issues 😅
Mabel: She said she knew this would happen LOL
Mabel: It's like a culture shock or something
Player: 😆
Mabel: So she sent me some money
Mabel: Oh and she sent a bit extra so we can have a nice lunch together today!
- Oh she really shouldn't have! [#Dollar] [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Date1Dollar\") == false]
	set PhoneUnlocks.claim = \"Date1Dollar\"
	Player: Oh she really shouldn't have!
- Oh she really shouldn't have! [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Date1Dollar\") == true]
	Player: Oh she really shouldn't have!
Mabel: Well she did!
Mabel: We're gonna have a super date!
Player: I'll be on my way in a bit
Mabel: Finallyy 🥰
Mabel: I'll change into something super cute
Player: Omw now
Player: Can't wait to see you!
do advance_time(4, 42)
if Story.mabel_trust < 50:
	do social_post(\"mabel_firstdate_ntr\")
else:
	do social_post(\"mabel_firstdate_nts\")
Mabel: I just got home
Mabel: Are you still on the bus?
Player: Yeah! It's still a long ride haha
Mabel: Omg I feel so bad 🥺
Mabel: But I kinda had an amazing time so.. I don't regret it 😇
Mabel: img: mabel/34
Mabel: Saving the cute outfit for you to look at later 😊
Player: I might put it up as my wallpaper!
Mabel: You wouldn't... would you? 🙈
Player: I guess you'll have to wait and see!
if Story.mabel_desire <= -6:
	Mabel: Omg and this cute photo you took for me too
	Mabel: img: mabel/35
	Mabel: You're like the cutest boyfriend ever seriously 🥰
	Mabel: PinkThought: I wish you leaned in and kissed me too
	Mabel: PinkThought: SERIOUSLY I'M INTERNALLY SCREAMING EEP
	Player: Aww shucks 😊
Player: Did you have a good time?
Mabel: I did!
Mabel: Omg the college cafe is like the cutest place ever
Player: It really was!
Mabel: And their cake was sooo adorable
Mabel: img: other/2
Mabel: I felt like a monster for eating something that cute 😭
Player: 🤣
Mabel: Did you have a good time?
Player: Of course!
Mabel: Good!
Mabel: I was a bit worried cause you only ordered coffee lol
Player: Hey I like coffee!
Mabel: Then we should do them more often hehe 😍
Mabel: Well with college for both of us and work starting for you... Will it be okay?
- It's gonna be tough
	Player: It's gonna be tough
	Player: I'll do my best though
	Mabel: I understand, please don't push yourself too hard for my sake
	Mabel: I mean I know I'm needy but I'll learn to give you space 😇
	Player: Thanks Mabel ❤️
- I'll make time for you anyway [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: I'll make time for you anyway
	Mabel: Seriously, you're gonna make a girl cry 😭❤️
	Mabel: I'll wait patiently for you to tell me when you're available 🫶
	Player: Sure thing Mabes
Mabel: I'm kinda nervous about tomorrow
Player: Of course you are! 😀
Mabel: Hey I can't help it!!
Mabel: I'm always nervous about everything all the time 😇
Player: Be careful, stress causes wrinkles!
Mabel: What!? IT DOES??
Mabel: Omg omg, that means I'm gonna get old fast!
Player: Better live life quickly then 😂
Mabel: True, I need to fill up my schedule with things to do
Mabel: Classes officially start so I better get planning
Player: You'll be fine
Mabel: Oh right, let me just mark all my classes on my map
Mabel: The campus is SO big so I'll have to make sure I know where I'm going 😋
Player: Good idea
Mabel: There! All done
Player: 👍
Mabel: Apart from my bed still being annoying, my room is pretty cozy now
Mabel: It feels like my secret agent hideout 😎
Mabel: Oh by the way
Mabel: Nina texted me this morning
Mabel: She said she had a great time at the club
Mabel: And that I should give it a chance
Mabel: She's asked me if I wanted to go next weekend  💀
Mabel: Thought: I don't know if I want to...
Player: What did you say?
Mabel: I haven't replied yet
Mabel: I do want to hang out again
Mabel: But I don't know if I want to try again 😅
Player: You can just tell her you'll consider it
Mabel: Omg true
Mabel: I'll see how the week goes and wait to see if you also have any free time hehe
Mabel: Thanks for talking this through with me 🥹
Mabel: Idk what I'd do without you
Player: Anytime 😊
Mabel: Alrighty I'm gonna head out and buy my stationary supplies and textbooks
Mabel: I've got so many things to do to prepare for tomorrow
Mabel: Wish me luck!
Player: Good luck!
Player: You're gonna do great!!
Mabel: I hope so 🥰
if Story.mabel_desire < 0:
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: And one last thing
	Player: Mhmm?
	Mabel: I love you ❤️
	Player: I love you too Mabes ❤️
	do heart(0)
Mabel: Hehe talk later!
Player: Later!
if Story.mabel_trust < 50:
	set Story.flag = \"mom2\"
	set PhoneUnlocks.leak = \"mom2\"
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
